        "description": {
            "value": "<p>At 7th level, you&rsquo;ve learned to attune your senses with nature. If you spend at least 1 minute meditating while in nature, you gain the following benefits for 1 hour:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You ignore difficult terrain caused by nature.</li>\n<li>You can understand plants within 30 feet of you. They can telepathically communicate simple ideas to you, including memories from within the past day.</li>\n<li>You can command plants within 30 feet of you to create difficult terrain, or other tasks at the GM&rsquo;s discretion (no action required).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you&rsquo;ve used this feature, you must complete a short or long rest before you can use it again.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
